<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ticket Portal | Registration Success</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 5px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #16a34a;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .button {
            display: block;
            width: 200px;
            background-color: #16a34a;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #15803d;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #d1d5db;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4b5563;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            console.log("Registration Success Page Loaded");
        });
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">Selamat Datang!</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Halo <%= username %>, Anda telah berhasil mendaftar!</p>
            <p>Berikut adalah informasi akun Anda:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Nama:</strong> <%= fullname %></li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></li>
                <li><strong>Tanggal Pendaftaran:</strong> <%= createdAt %></li>
            </ul>
            <p>Untuk memulai silahkan klik tombol di bawah ini:</p>
            <a href="<%= activationLink %>" class="button">Aktifkan Akun</a>
            <p>Jika anda mengalami kesulitan silahkan hubungi kami.</p>
            <p>Salam hangat, Tim Admin Ticket Portal</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">&copy; 2025 Ticket Portal. All Rights Reserved.</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
